# Attacker Ne Todha Nahi — Seedha Login Kar Liya
## Blackpoint Cyber 2026 Annual Threat Report — Ek Developer Ki Nazar Se

---

*"Ek valid username. Ek sahi password. Aur woh tool jo tumhari team roz use karti hai. 2025 mein yahi cheezein attacker ka welcome mat ban gayi."*
— Gagan Singh, CEO, Blackpoint Cyber

---

Ek second ke liye imagine karo.

Tumne mahino laga diye apni infrastructure harden karne mein. Firewall rules, rate limiting, WAF policies, har jagah MFA. Tumhe achha lag raha hai. Tumhe *secure* feel ho raha hai. Phir ek Tuesday dopahar ko — ek attacker seedha tumhare front door se andar aa jaata hai.

Firewall fail nahi hua. MFA bypass nahi hua. Koi zero-day use nahi hua.

Bas ek valid VPN credential tha. Ek RMM tool install kiya jo tumhari IT team already use karti hai. Aur woh bilkul ek normal employee ki tarah dikh raha tha, normal kaam karte hue.

Yeh koi hypothetical nahi hai. **Yahi 2025 tha.**

