## Pehle Jaano: Yeh Report Hai Kya, Aur Kisne Publish Ki?

**Blackpoint Cyber** ek US-based cybersecurity company hai jo **24/7 human-led Security Operations Center (SOC)** operate karti hai. Yeh mainly **Managed Service Providers (MSPs)** ko serve karti hai — matlab woh companies jo doosri companies ka IT manage karti hain.

Unka kaam hai har waqt real environments mein hone wale attacks ko detect karna aur rokna. Automated tools se nahi — trained humans se jo context samjhte hain, sirf alerts nahi padhte.

Har saal woh apna **Annual Threat Report** publish karte hain — jo unke SOC ne us puri saal mein handle kiye real incidents ke data pe based hota hai. Koi academic research nahi. Koi synthetic data nahi. Real intrusions, real kill chains, real case studies.

**Yeh hai 2026 Annual Threat Report** — covering January 2025 to December 2025.

> 📄 **Source:** *Blackpoint Cyber 2026 Annual Threat Report* — published by Blackpoint Cyber (blackpointcyber.com). Full PDF **MonkeyPatching GitHub repository** pe available hai — link article ke end mein hai. Jao, original padho, worth it hai.

