## Defenders Ko Kya Karna Chahiye: Priority Order Mein

Report ki recommendations, developer lens se filter karke:

### Abhi Karo (Aaj)

- **VPNs pe MFA universally enforce karo** — koi exception nahi, koi legacy fallback nahi
- **VPN address pools strictly segment karo** — remote sessions domain controllers, backup servers, ya RMM infrastructure tak directly nahi pahunchni chahiye

### Is Hafte Karo

- **`%APPDATA%`, `%TEMP%`, aur `Downloads` se execution block karo** — report ke almost every installer-based attack ka payload staging location yahi tha
- **Uncommon TLDs block karo** — `.online`, `.top`, `.live` disproportionately RMM C2 infrastructure mein use hote hain
- **Outbound Web3 RPC endpoints block karo** (Binance Smart Chain JSON-RPC) — yeh directly Etherhiding delivery break karta hai

### Is Quarter Mein Karo

- **Phishing-resistant MFA (FIDO2 / WebAuthn) pe migrate karo** — regular TOTP AiTM nahi rokta. Hardware keys ya passkeys rokti hain
- **Standard users ke liye `Win+R` GPO se disable karo** — ClickFix execution bridge remove ho jaata hai
- **Immutable backups with off-network replication implement karo** — ransomware ka final leverage disappear ho jaata hai jab tum bina payment ke recover kar sako

