## Woh Insight Jo Koi Nahi Baat Karta

Report ke statistics mein ek cheez buried hai jo zyada attention deserve karti hai:

**56% of all incidents were disrupted before a payload was deployed.**

Yeh EDR nahi tha ek known malware signature catch karte hue. Yeh humans the jo behavioral context dekh rahe the:

- VPN session unusual subnet se domain controller hit kar raha hai authentication ke seconds baad
- ScreenConnect install kar raha hai `msiexec` spawn karke doosra RMM installer fetch karne ke liye
- User Run dialog se curl command run kar raha hai

Yeh behaviors individually malicious nahi hain. Yeh contextually suspicious hain jab tum baseline jaante ho.

**Attacker paradox:** Zero-days aur exotic exploits abandon karke trusted tooling mein shift karke, attackers ne khud ko actually zyada detectable banaya, kam nahi. Jitna zyada woh normal behavior mein blend hote hain, utna important ho jaata hai ki defenders ko *pata ho* normal behavior kaisi dikhti hai.

Agar 2025 woh saal tha jab attackers ne trust weaponize kiya — toh 2026 woh saal hona chahiye jab defenders context awareness build karein.

