## Closing Thought: Tumhara Code Is Mein Part Hai

Ek baat jo developers kam sunte hain:

Top five CWE categories mein se teen — deserialization, path traversal, authentication bypass — woh cheezein hain jo **tumhare likhe code mein hoti hain**. Network hardware mein nahi jo tum configure karte ho. Security team ki policies mein nahi. Us function mein jo tumne last Tuesday likha tha.

2025 mein 45,000 CVEs sirf legacy hardware se nahi aaye. Bahut saare applications se aaye. APIs. Web apps. File processing services. Woh cheezein jo developers ne build kiyaan.

Security building khatam karne ke baad nahi hoti. Yeh ek constraint hai jiske around tum design karte ho — same way jaise performance ya scalability ke around karte ho. Yeh report ek window hai us cheez mein jo hota hai jab yeh nahi hota.

